*** ''Oryzorictes tetradactylus''
* [[馬島蝟亞科|馬島蝟亞科]] ''Tenrecinae''
** [[小馬島蝟屬|小馬島蝟屬]] ''Echinops''
*** ''Echinops telfairi''
** [[紋蝟屬|紋蝟屬]] ''Hemicentetes''
*** ''Hemicentetes nigriceps''
*** [[低地紋蝟|低地紋蝟]]''Hemicentetes semispinosus''
